<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠١٧٥ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ الثَّوْرِيَّ،<span class="c5"> وَعِمْرَانَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا يَرَيَانِ بِمُصَافَحَةِ الْيَهُودِيِّ وَالنَّصْرَانِيِّ بَأْسًا»</span>.<span class="c5"> قَالَ عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ:</span> <span class="c2">«وَلَا بَأْسَ بِهِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>